OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy skies
OL,6,Freturning into Wednesday evening, with
OL,7,Fareas of mist and fog developing
OL,8,Fthrough the night. Chilly, with an
OL,9,Fisolated frost likely as winds fall
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,13,Ffog soon clearing back to coasts to
OL,14,Fgive another fine and dry day with
OL,15,Flong sunny spells and light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,18,Ffine and warm during this period with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunny spells and light
OL,20,Fwinds. Chilly at times overnight with
OL,21,Fsome patchy overnight fog possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
